Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,值多少...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How much...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么精美的相框，你觉得呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Does a fine frame like that cost, do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没跟你说过，可你喝醉时说话有点像瑟斯博士{\fs12}美国著名儿童作家{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I never told you, but you sound a little like Dr. Seuss when you're drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道，我是认真问的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I know. I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是认真的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Serious, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得说价值最少得几百\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'd say it cost at least a couple hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要给你读一下\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm gonna read it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说话真的像瑟斯博士吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Do I really sound like Dr. Seuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“为表彰他在儿童心理学领域之杰出成就\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}"In recognition of his outstanding achievement in the field of child psychology."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.75,0:05:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“他对工作的尽心尽力，以及他持续致力于提高生活品质...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}His dedication to his work and his continuing efforts to improve the quality of life..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你专心点好吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Will you concentrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“他持续致力于提高生活品质...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}"...his continuing efforts to improve the quality of life...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“为了无数儿童及其家人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}"for countless children and their families,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“费城市府荣幸颁予费城之子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}"the city of Philadelphia proudly bestows upon its son...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“马尔科姆·克劳医生” 就是你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Dr. Malcolm Crowe..." That's you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“优异专业市长嘉奖”\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}"...the Mayor's Citation for professional excellence."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们称你为费城之子呢\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They called you their son.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们该把它挂到卫生间去\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We should hang it in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这对我们是重要的一晚\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is an important night for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于，有人认识到你所做的牺牲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Finally, someone is recognizing the sacrifices you've made...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把什么都放在第二位，包括我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}that you have put everything second, including me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只为了他们所说的那些家庭\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}for those families that they're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:05:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也说明我丈夫有天份\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They're also saying that my husband has a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有天分，教导孩子们...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You have a gift that teaches children...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何坚强面对，连多数成人都会尿裤子的处境\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}how to be strong in situations... Where most adults would piss on themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信他们写的是真的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I believe what they wrote is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想用玻璃杯盛些酒\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I would like some wine in a glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.26,0:06:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想盛在马克杯里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I would not like it in a mug.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想盛在罐子里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I would not like it in a jug.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安娜，不要动，不要出一点声\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Anna, don't move. Don't make a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是罗克斯街47号\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is 47 Locus Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打破了一扇窗户，闯入私人住宅\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You've broken a window and entered a private residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道太多事情\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You don't know so many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:08:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这所房子里没有针头或任何类型的处方药物\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}There are no needles or prescription drugs of any kind in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你独处时为什么会害怕吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Do you know why you're afraid when you're alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I do. I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他许诺我的，我想要他许诺我的东西\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What he promised me! I want what he promised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，我的天\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认识你吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Do I know you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不认识我吗，英雄？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't you know me, hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你连自己的病人都不记得了？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't you even remember your own patients?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,市区诊所\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Downtown clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,单亲家庭\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Single-parent family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能有情绪障碍\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Possible mood disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.74,0:08:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我那时害怕\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I was afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉我，我在处理父母离婚上有问题\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You told me I was having trouble coping with my parents'divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:08:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你错了 你错了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You were wrong. You were wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在看看我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Now look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我再也不想要害怕  - 给我一分钟想想\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- I don't want to be afraid no more. - Just give me a minute to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我等了你十年\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I waited ten years for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也不给你了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm not giving you nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本·弗里德金？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Ben Friedkin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些人，他们叫我怪胎\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Some people, they call me "freak."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.61,0:09:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赖安·萨姆纳?\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Ryan Sumner?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是，我就是个怪胎，瞧瞧我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I am. I am a freak. Look at...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文森特\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文森特·格雷\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincent Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，你不要\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的确记得你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I do remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安静，非常聪明\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Quiet, very smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有同情心\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Compassionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不同寻常的同情心\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Unusually compassionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了说“受诅咒的”\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You forgot cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没治好我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You failed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没治好我!\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You failed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文森特，很抱歉如果我不是...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincent, I'm sorry if I wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.45,0:10:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我没帮到你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}if I didn't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但要是你能...让我试试\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But if you just let me try,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你能给我一个机会\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}if you just give me a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢，上帝啊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, God! Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 文森特有没有...  - 别说话，嘘\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Did Vincent... - Don't talk. Shh.

Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:12:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的，科尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's okay, Cole.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是马尔科姆·克劳医生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My name is Dr. Malcolm Crowe.
