Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.17,0:13:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗，过去在欧洲，人们曾经躲进教堂\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know, in the olden days in Europe, people used to hide out in churches.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会要求避难\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They would claim sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在躲什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What were they hiding from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲坏人，多数情况下\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Bad people, mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些人想把他们关进监狱，伤害他们\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}People that wanted to put them in jail, hurt them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我注意到你的眼镜，上面并没有镜片\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I noticed your eyeglasses. They don't have any lenses in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我爸的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They're my dad's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,镜片让我眼睛不舒服\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The lenses hurt my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我进来的时候你在跟你的士兵们说什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What were you talking about with your soldiers when I came in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“得...”\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Day...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.35,0:14:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,De profundus clamo adite domine
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这叫拉丁语\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's called "Latin."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你的士兵们都说拉丁语吗？ - 不\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- All your soldiers speak Latin? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.03,0:14:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是好医生吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Are you a good doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经是\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有一次得过一张奖状，市长颁发的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I won an award once from the mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它的框很贵\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It had an expensive frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.37,0:14:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会再见到你，对吧？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm gonna see you again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你觉得可以的话\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If that's okay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，早上好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.63,0:17:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cole.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cole!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，你的巧克力脆片都软掉了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, your Cocoa Puffs are gettin' soggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Let me see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，亲爱的，你这儿有污点，抬头\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Let me see you. Oh, honey, you got a spot. Head up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，可以了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Okay, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.98,0:18:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在找什么吗，宝贝？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Something you were looking for, baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.05,0:18:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夹心馅饼？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Pop Tarts?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在这儿\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They're right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么，妈妈？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, what are you thinking, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.63,0:18:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Lots of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有关我的不是？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Anything bad about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，看着我的脸\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, look at my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没在想你的不是\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I was not thinking something bad about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.31,0:18:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:18:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.75,0:19:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来，抬起头\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Here, head up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那是汤米  - 好了，你把它塞进去 科尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- That's Tommy. - That's okay. You tuck it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科尔，你要这个吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cole, you want this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，怪胎，你觉得搭肩膀那招如何？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, freak, how'd you like that "arm around the shoulder" bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我刚装出来的，我发挥了一下\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I just made that up. I went with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好演员都这么做，这叫即兴表演\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's what great actors do. It's called "improv."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，宝贝\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天怎么样？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How was your day?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.35,0:20:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的，需要的话你可以跟我讲讲的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know, you can tell me things if you need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.23,0:20:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我今天做什么了吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, you know what I did today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...早上赢了宾州彩票\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I, uh, I won the Pennsylvania Lottery in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.30,0:20:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我辞掉了我那些工作\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I quit my jobs,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:21:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接着我去公园大野餐，吃了好多巧克力慕斯派\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and I ate a big picnic in the park with lots of chocolate mousse pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我整个下午在喷泉里游泳\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And then I swam in the fountain all afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What'd you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.43,0:21:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被第一个选入课间球队\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I was picked first for kick ball teams at recess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打了支满垒全垒打赢下比赛\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I hit a grand slam to win the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家把我举在肩上，扛着我绕圈，欢呼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Everybody lifted me up on their shoulders and carried me around, cheering.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，那样的话，我要给你做些三角煎饼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, in that case, I am gonna make you some triangle pancakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.12,0:21:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你一个钟头\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You got an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.01,0:21:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想坐吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Wanna sit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天不想谈吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't feel like talking today?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:21:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想玩个游戏吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Wanna play a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是个读心游戏\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's a mind-reading game.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.05,0:22:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样玩的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Here's how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来读你的心\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I read your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.65,0:22:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我说对了，你就朝椅子走一步\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If what I say is right, you take one step towards the chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.74,0:22:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我说错了，你就后退一步，朝门口\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If what I say is wrong, you take one step back... towards the doorway.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.12,0:22:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你走到椅子旁，就坐下\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If you reach the chair, you sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你退到门口，就可以走\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If you reach the door, you can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.17,0:22:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想玩吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Wanna play?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.20,0:22:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.04,0:22:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你母亲和父亲刚离婚时\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}When your mother and father were first divorced,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.46,0:23:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈去看过我这种医生，可他帮不了她\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}your mom went to see a doctor like me, and he didn't help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.73,0:23:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你觉得我也不能帮你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}So you think I'm not going to be able to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.02,0:23:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你担心 她说她跟医生说了一些事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're worried that she said she told him things...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.05,0:23:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一些她不能跟其他人说的事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}things she couldn't tell anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.52,0:23:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一些秘密\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.70,0:23:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有一个秘密，但你不想告诉我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You have a secret, but you don't want to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.80,0:23:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸走之前把那只表给你作礼物\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your dad gave you that watch as a present just before he went away.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.21,0:24:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他把它忘在抽屉里了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He forgot it in a drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.03,0:24:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坏了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.77,0:24:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在学校一直很安静，但...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You keep pretty quiet in school, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.11,0:24:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是个好学生，你从没真正惹过什么大麻烦\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}you're a good student, you've never really been in any serious trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.29,0:24:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一次我们要画一幅画\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We were supposed to draw a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.00,0:24:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想画什么都行\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Anything we wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.60,0:24:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我画了一个人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I drew a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.50,0:24:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他脖子受伤了，另一个人用螺丝刀干的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He got hurt in the neck by another man with a screwdriver.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.11,0:25:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在电视上看到的吗，科尔？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You saw that on TV, Cole?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.00,0:25:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人人都很不安\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Everyone got upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.97,0:25:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们开了个会\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They had a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.85,0:25:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈开始哭\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mom started crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.66,0:25:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不那样画了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't draw like that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.30,0:25:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在怎么画呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How do you draw now?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.67,0:25:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我画…人们在微笑\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I draw... people smiling,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.21,0:25:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狗在奔跑\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}dogs running,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.81,0:25:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彩虹\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}rainbows.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.90,0:25:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不会为了彩虹开会\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They don't have meetings about rainbows.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.09,0:25:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错，我想是不会\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No. I guess they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.09,0:25:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在在想什么?\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What am I thinking now?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.67,0:25:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你在想什么\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't know what you're thinking now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.17,0:26:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.21,0:26:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你人是好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}you're nice,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.05,0:26:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可你帮不了我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}but you can't help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.84,0:26:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你说的是另一家意大利餐厅，我向你求婚那家\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I thought you meant the other Italian restaurant I asked you to marry me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.41,0:26:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，安娜\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm so sorry, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.83,0:26:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好像就是掌握不好时间\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I just can't seem to keep track of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.20,0:26:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且今天的访谈也不太好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And I didn't have a very good session today.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.52,0:26:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们俩多么相似\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They're both so similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.46,0:27:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同样的小习惯，同样的表情，脑子里悬着同样的事情\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The same mannerisms, same expressions, same things hanging over their head.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.24,0:27:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想可能是某种虐待\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I think it might be some kind of abuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.82,0:27:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科尔的手臂上有抓痕\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cole has... scratches on his arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.58,0:27:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想可能是指甲抓伤\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I think they might be fingernail cuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.12,0:27:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,防卫伤，也许，我不知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Defensive cuts, maybe. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.10,0:27:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是个老师或邻居\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Maybe a teacher or a neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.70,0:27:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为不是他母亲，我已见过她和他相处，看起来不符合\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't think it's the mother. I've seen her with him, and it doesn't seem to fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.59,0:27:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可能只是我搞错了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Or I could just be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.80,0:27:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许他只是个很喜欢爬树的孩子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Maybe he's just a kid who likes to climb trees a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.11,0:27:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安娜\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.75,0:27:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我这段时间有点疏远，好吗\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I know that I've been a little distant, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.71,0:27:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这让你生气，我只是...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I know that it makes you mad. I just...
