Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.95,0:29:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁跟你这么说你都不要相信，那是屁话\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't you believe anybody that tries to convince you of that. That's bullshit.
