Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.25,0:31:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,举个例子，一个人可能会把东西留在桌上，让别人找到\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}For example, a person might leave something on the desk for someone else to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.52,0:31:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道自由联想书写是什么吗，科尔？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Do you know what free association writing is, Cole?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.36,0:31:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.58,0:31:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自由联想书写就是拿起一支笔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Free association writing is when you take a pencil in your hand, and
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.73,0:31:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把笔放在一张纸上，开始书写\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}you put the pencil to a piece of paper and you start writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.45,0:31:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不去看或是想你在写什么\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And you don't look at what you're writing or think about what you're writing.
