Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.07,0:31:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能会是...你在别的地方听说的事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It could be something you heard somewhere else,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.66,0:31:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是...藏在你内心深处的感觉\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}or feelings you had deep inside of you.
