Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.97,0:32:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你都写些什么?\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What did you write?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.65,0:32:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不安的词语\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Upset words.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.35,0:32:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你爸离开前，你写过什么不安的词语吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Did you ever write any upset words before your father left?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.75,0:32:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不记得了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.20,0:32:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能为我做件事吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Can you do something for me?
