Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.10,0:32:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们的目标应该是什么\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}what our goal should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.71,0:32:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,某件我想要的东西？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Something I want?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.37,0:32:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能改变你人生中的某件事，什么东西都行\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If you could change something in your life, anything at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.84,0:32:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会要什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}what would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.05,0:32:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不算我想要的，可不可以是我不想要的？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Instead of something I want, can it be something I don't want?
