Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.22,0:32:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要再害怕\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't want to be scared anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.11,0:33:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去开门吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You gonna get that?
