Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.62,0:33:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教教我怎么买那些东西\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and show me how to buy at one of these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.60,0:33:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道今天能不能对付亚米希人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't know if I can deal with the Amish today.
