Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.54,0:34:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1790到1800年间美利坚合众国的首都是哪里？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}what city was capital of the United States of America from 1790 to 1800?
