Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.85,0:35:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有人猜一下，一百年前这栋建筑是做什么用的？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Can anyone guess what this building was used for a hundred years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.40,0:35:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你来上学之前，甚至在我来这儿上学之前\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}before you went to school here, before I went to this school even?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.90,0:35:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说吧，科尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yes, Cole.
