Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.40,0:35:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们把人拉进来，犯人哭着跟亲人亲吻告别\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They pulled the people in, crying and kissing their families bye.
