Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.34,0:42:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 查克什么？  - 芝士，是个小孩去的地方\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Chucky who? - Cheese. It's a kids place.
