Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.95,0:42:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面有人吗?\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Is someone out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.22,0:42:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请打开这扇门\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Open this door, please. Come on.
