Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.37,0:44:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.80,0:44:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我出去，不...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Let me out! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.41,0:44:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不！不！\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.43,0:44:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科尔？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cole?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.90,0:44:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cole!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.18,0:44:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这门有钥匙吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Is there a key for this door?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.26,0:45:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科尔？亲爱的，听得见我吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cole? Honey? Honey, can you hear me?
