Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.56,0:48:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他爱这工作\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He loved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.19,0:48:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他爱这工作甚于一切\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He loved it more than anything else.
