Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.20,0:48:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对其中一个孩子犯了错误\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}mistake with one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.61,0:48:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他帮不了那个孩子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He couldn't help that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.14,0:48:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他自责不已\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And he can't stop thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.81,0:48:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他...无法忘怀\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He can't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.22,0:49:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从那时起，事情都变了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Ever since then, things have been different.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.32,0:49:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不再是以前那个人了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's not the same person that he used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.66,0:49:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而他的妻子...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And his wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.67,0:49:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢变了以后的这个人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}doesn't like the person that he's become.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.23,0:49:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们几乎不再交谈，就像陌生人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They barely speak anymore. They're like strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.30,0:49:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后来有一天，马尔科姆遇见一个了不得的小男孩\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And then one day, Malcolm meets this wonderful little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.24,0:49:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个很棒的小男孩\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A really cool little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.01,0:49:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他想起另一个孩子的许多\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Reminds him a lot of the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.08,0:49:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马尔科姆决定试着去帮助这个新的男孩\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And Malcolm decides to try and help this new boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.35,0:49:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他感觉如果能帮助这个新男孩\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}'cause he feels that if he can help this new boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.33,0:49:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就像是...也帮助了另外那个\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}it will be like... helping that other one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.53,0:49:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这故事的结局如何？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How does the story end?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.73,0:49:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.62,0:50:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我想告诉你我的秘密了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I wanna tell you my secret now.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.80,0:50:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.77,0:50:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能看见死人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I see dead people.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.21,0:50:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在梦里吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}In your dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.68,0:50:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你醒着的时候？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}While you're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.16,0:50:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死人，就像是，在坟墓里的，棺材里的？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Dead people, like, in graves, in coffins?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.53,0:50:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像普通人一样走来走去\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Walking around like regular people.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.97,0:50:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们互相看不见\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They don't see each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.57,0:51:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们只看得见他们想看到的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They only see what they wanna see.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.60,0:51:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不知道自己已经死了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They don't know they're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.04,0:51:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你多常见到他们？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How often do you see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.75,0:51:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时时刻刻\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}All the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.72,0:51:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们无处不在\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They're everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.63,0:51:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会跟别人说我的秘密，对吧？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You won't tell anyone my secret, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.80,0:51:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会，我保证\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.40,0:51:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能等我睡着再走吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Will you stay here until I fall asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.47,0:51:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.02,0:51:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科尔...的病情比最初的评估更严重\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cole has pathologies more severe than initially assessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.59,0:51:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他受到幻觉困扰\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's suffering from visual hallucinations,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.60,0:51:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妄想症\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}paranoia,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.46,0:52:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,某种学龄儿童的精神分裂症\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Some kind of... school-age schizophrenia.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.47,0:52:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,药物治疗，住院治疗，也许是需要的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Medication, hospitalization may be required.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.64,0:52:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对他没有帮助\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And I'm not helping him.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.97,0:53:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，我是琳恩·希尔，科尔的妈妈\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hi, this is Lynn Sear, Cole's mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.27,0:53:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，我想跟你谈谈...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah, uh, l... I'd like to talk to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.01,0:53:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你儿子和他的朋友，别再碰我儿子...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}about your boy and his friends keeping their goddamn hands off my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.55,0:55:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.05,0:55:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，晚饭还没好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, dinner is not ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.25,0:55:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.41,0:55:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你再不能伤害我了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You can't hurt me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.81,0:55:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奈迪，你是个可怕的丈夫，奈迪！\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Neddy! You're a terrible husband, Neddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.13,0:55:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看你逼我干了什么，奈迪\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Look what you made me do! Neddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.52,0:56:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从前有个男孩\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Once there was a boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.89,0:56:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和其他男孩完全不同\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}very different from all the other boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.82,0:56:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他住在丛林里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He lived in the jungle,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.76,0:56:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他还能跟动物说话\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and he could speak to the animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.50,0:56:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得这出戏烂透了吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Did you think the play sucked big time?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.50,0:56:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.27,0:56:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤米·汤马西诺演过一个咳嗽药广告\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Tommy Tammisimo acted in a cough syrup commercial.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.58,0:56:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说大家都演得自觉而不实在\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He said everyone was self-conscious and unrealistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.58,0:56:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他还说这出戏烂透了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He said the play sucked big time.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.18,0:56:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个叫汤米的小孩好像很讨人厌\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This Tommy kid sounds like a real punk.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.42,0:57:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这出戏很精彩，比《猫》还棒\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I thought the play was excellent. Better than "Cats."
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.49,0:57:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 《猫》？  - 算了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- "Cats"? - Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.46,0:57:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科尔，我对你在医院里跟我说的话很感兴趣\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cole, I was really interested in what you told me at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.12,0:57:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想再多听一些\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'd like to hear more about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.45,0:57:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科尔？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cole?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.95,0:57:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.26,0:57:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那边有什么东西？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Is something up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.94,0:57:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cole,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.11,0:57:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也没看见\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.62,0:58:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待着别动\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Be real still.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.32,0:58:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时你从内心感觉到\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Sometimes you feel it inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.71,0:58:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像你在快速下坠\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}like you're falling down real fast,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.46,0:58:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但其实你只是站着没动\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}but you're really just standing still.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.13,0:58:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你曾感觉过后脖梗发凉吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You ever feel the prickly things on the back of your neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.40,0:58:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.44,0:58:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有你胳膊上的汗毛，根根直立？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And the tiny hairs on your arm, you know, when they stand up?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.41,0:58:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.64,0:58:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是他们\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's them.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.96,0:58:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当他们生气时\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}When they get mad,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.16,0:58:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就开始冷\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}it gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.37,0:59:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没看到什么，你确定他们在那边吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't see anything. Are you sure they're there?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.80,0:59:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cole?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.02,0:59:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你叫他们走开\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Please make them leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.87,0:59:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在努力\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm workin' on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.28,0:59:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.44,1:00:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈，爸爸\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mommy, Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.87,1:00:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的喉咙好疼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My throat hurts.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.35,1:00:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小儿止咳糖浆\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Pedia Ease cough suppressant.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.38,1:00:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,温和，快速，有效...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Gentle, fast, effect...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.27,1:00:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cole.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.73,1:00:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不管他们怎么说，这东西坏了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't care what they say, this thing is broken.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.82,1:00:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脱掉\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Take 'em off.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.76,1:00:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要放在餐桌上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't want them on my table.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.75,1:01:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打扫时看见你衣柜抽屉里有什么了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I saw what was in your bureau drawer when I was cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.83,1:01:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要不要坦白一下？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Got something you want to confess?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.50,1:01:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那只大黄蜂链坠\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The bumblebee pendant?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.52,1:01:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么老是拿走它？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Why do you keep taking it?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.91,1:01:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是外婆的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It was Grandma's.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.28,1:01:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道，万一摔坏了呢？你知道我会多难过\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know, what if it broke? You know how sad I'd be.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.76,1:01:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会哭，因为你非常想念外婆\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You'd cry 'cause you miss Grandma so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.83,1:01:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.07,1:01:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候，人们以为丢失了东西\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Sometimes people think they lose things,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.47,1:01:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实没有失去，只是被移走了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and they really didn't lose them... it just gets moved.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.21,1:01:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你移走了大黄蜂链坠吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}So, did you move the bumblebee pendant?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.28,1:02:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要生气\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't get mad.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.21,1:02:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么这次是谁移走的？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}So, who moved it this time?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.21,1:02:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许是别人进了咱们家，把大黄蜂链坠拿出我的衣柜\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Maybe someone came in our house, took the bumblebee pendant out of my closet...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.23,1:02:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再好好放进你的抽屉里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and placed it nicely in your drawer.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.62,1:02:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许是\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.20,1:02:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天，我很累了，科尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}God, I am so tired, Cole.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.12,1:02:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我身体累，我脑子也累\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm tired in my body, I'm tired in my mind,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.90,1:02:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的...心里也累了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm... tired in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.77,1:02:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要帮助\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I need some help.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.04,1:02:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你注意到没有，咱们的小家状况并不太好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know, I don't know if you noticed, but our little family isn't doing so good.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.25,1:02:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说，我一直在祷告\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I mean, I've been praying,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.31,1:02:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可一定是我没祷告对\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}but I must not be praying right.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.25,1:02:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们只能互相回应对方的祈祷\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Looks like we're just gonna have to answer each other's prayers.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.00,1:02:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我们不能好好交流，我们就不可能做到\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If we can't talk to each other, we're not gonna make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.66,1:02:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在告诉我，宝贝，我不会生气的，宝贝\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Now, tell me, baby. I won't get mad, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.30,1:02:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有拿大黄蜂链坠？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Did you take the bumblebee pendant?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.37,1:03:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.56,1:03:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你吃够多的烤牛肉了，你得离开餐桌了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You've had enough roast beef. You need to leave the table.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.92,1:03:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去！\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.04,1:03:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，过来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.64,1:03:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你看我爸藏枪的地方，来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'll show you where my dad keeps his gun. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.31,1:03:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塞巴斯蒂安，过来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Sebastian, come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.86,1:03:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mama?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.50,1:03:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不是特别生气\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If you're not very mad,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.21,1:04:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今晚能不能睡你床上？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}can I sleep in your bed tonight?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.61,1:04:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着我的脸\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Look at my face.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.23,1:04:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有特别生气\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm not very mad.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.52,1:04:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝，你怎么在发抖？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Baby, why are you shaking?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.12,1:04:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科尔，怎么了?\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cole, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.43,1:04:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，上帝，求你告诉我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, God, please tell me!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.83,1:04:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.51,1:04:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是爱德华时期的...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's Edwardian
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.39,1:04:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精工制作，矿式切割的碎钻和一颗真彩缅甸蓝宝石\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}beautifully worked with mine-cut diamonds and an actual color Burmese sapphire.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.82,1:04:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永恒久远\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's timeless.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.23,1:04:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.60,1:04:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有普通一点的？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Got anything a little plainer?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.30,1:04:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普通点？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Plainer?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.60,1:05:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要个普通的钻戒来配你那普通的未婚妻，是这样吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You want a plain ring to go with your plain fiance? Is that how it is?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.17,1:05:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是，宝贝，别会错了意思\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No! Baby, don't get in a tissy.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.24,1:05:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这么漂亮\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Uh... You're so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.01,1:05:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你本身就像一颗缅甸蓝宝石\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're like a Burmese sapphire all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.66,1:05:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要这些\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You don't need all that.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.72,1:05:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们为什么不试戴一下\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Why don't you try it on...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.33,1:05:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看你俩对它感觉如何？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and see how you both feel about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.03,1:05:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞧，感觉怎么样？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}There. How does that feel?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.43,1:05:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这枚钻戒，传达出一种渴望\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I think this piece, um, communicates a longing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.71,1:05:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想象那个曾经拥有它的女人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I imagine that the woman who owned it...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.91,1:05:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱上了一个无法在一起的男人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}loved a man that she couldn't be with.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.43,1:05:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她有卷发和栗色眼睛吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Did he have wavy hair and chestnut eyes?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.92,1:05:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，我不知道，但...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Um, I don't know, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.78,1:05:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这店里很多首饰都能沟通\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}a lot of the pieces in this store communicate,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.11,1:06:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为你们应该选一件跟你交谈的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and I think you should choose a piece that speaks to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.73,1:06:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想，也许当人们拥有过东西，在他们去世后\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I think maybe when people own things and then they pass away,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.57,1:06:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的一部分会复印在那些东西上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}a part of themselves gets printed on those things,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.13,1:06:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像...像是指纹\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}like... like fingerprints.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.95,1:06:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把它包起来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'll just wrap it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.93,1:06:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要一个有硕士文凭的伙计\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You don't need a guy with a Master's.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.18,1:06:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你需要一个脖子比脑袋粗的摔角手\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You need a wrestler with a neck larger than his head.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.39,1:06:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我需要一个有硕士文凭的摔角手\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, I need a wrestler with a Master's.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.41,1:06:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这是什么？  - 生日快乐\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- What's this? - Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.07,1:06:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你送的？  - 嗯\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- For me? - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.01,1:06:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是本...初版书\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's a... first edition.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.70,1:06:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这太贵了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know, this is too much.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.40,1:06:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，从你的圣诞奖金里扣\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No. Took it out of your Christmas bonus.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.20,1:07:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完美的礼物，安娜\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's perfect, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.10,1:07:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.12,1:07:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有东西里你最想要的是什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What do you want more than anything?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.13,1:07:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.24,1:07:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说过我想要什么\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I've told you what I want.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.94,1:07:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我想要什么\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I know what I want.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.91,1:07:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想能够再跟我妻子交谈\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I want to be able to talk to my wife again.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.00,1:07:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就跟我们以前那样交谈\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The way we used to talk to each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.25,1:07:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像世上没有别人，只有我们\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Like there was no one else in the world except us.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.36,1:07:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎么做？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How are you gonna do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.71,1:07:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能再当你的医生了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Can't be your doctor anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.87,1:07:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有给自己家人足够的关心\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I haven't paid enough attention to my family.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.51,1:07:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样做就会出问题\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Bad things happen when you do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.21,1:07:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懂吗?\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.21,1:08:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我会转走你，我认识两个心理医生...  - 别放弃我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- I'm going to transfer you. I know two psychologists. - Don't fail me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.21,1:08:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别放弃，你是唯一能帮助我的人，我知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't give up. You're the only one who can help me, I know it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.46,1:08:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帮不了你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I can't help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.00,1:08:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你...你...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.52,1:08:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有其他人能帮你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Someone else can help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.04,1:08:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你相信我，对吧？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You believe me, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.80,1:08:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳医生，你相信我的秘密，对吧？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Dr. Crowe, you believe my secret, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.57,1:08:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道该怎么回答，科尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't know how to answer that, Cole.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.56,1:08:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么能帮我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How can you help me...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.63,1:08:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不相信我？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}if you don't believe me?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.60,1:09:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些魔术是真的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Some magic's real.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.30,1:09:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你独处时为什么会害怕吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Do you know why you're afraid when you're alone?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.63,1:09:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I do. I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.64,1:09:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉，文森特，希望我没离开你太久\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm sorry about that, Vincent. I hope I didn't leave you alone too long.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.31,1:09:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里好冷\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Whew. It's cold in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.71,1:09:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文森特，你为什么在哭？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincent, why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.88,1:09:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会相信的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You won't believe.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.93,1:10:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉，文森特，希望我没离开你太久\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm sorry about that, Vincent. I hope I didn't leave you alone too long.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.60,1:10:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里好冷\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Whew. It's cold in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.04,1:10:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文森特...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincent...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.61,1:10:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里好冷\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Whew. It's cold in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.52,1:10:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，知道吗？我也从来不喜欢他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Nah, you know what? I never liked him either.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.31,1:10:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我小时候，有一次验血\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}When I was a kid, I had this blood test done,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.97,1:10:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把辣椒芝士薯条吐了女护士一身\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and I threw up chili cheese fries all over this male nurse.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.85,1:10:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了，里德医生在2线\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Excuse me. Dr. Reed is on line two.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.48,1:10:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文森特，请原谅，我得接这个电话\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincent, will you excuse me? I have to take this.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.40,1:10:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 给我一分钟时间，好吗？  - 好的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Just give me a minute, okay? -Okay
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.05,1:12:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo no quiero morir\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yo no quiero morir.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.00,1:12:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo no quiero morir\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yo no quiero morir.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.70,1:12:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢，我的天\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.12,1:12:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在到处跑？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You been running around?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.00,1:12:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你感觉好受些？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Make you feel better?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.62,1:12:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢到处跑，很好的锻炼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I like to run around. It's good exercise.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.91,1:12:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在想问我问题吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Do you want to ask me questions now?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.49,1:12:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想当M连的准下士吗，陆战队第七师第三营\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Want to be a lance corporal in Company "M, " Third Battalion, Seventh Marines?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.23,1:12:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚被派到广南省{\fs12}越南{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We're being dispatched into the Quang Nam province.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.13,1:12:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Maybe later.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.86,1:12:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有事发生了，对吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Something happened, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.90,1:12:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很激动？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You wigging out?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.11,1:13:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，我想是吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yes. I think I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.92,1:13:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道“Yo no quiero morir”什么意思吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Do you know what "Yo no quiero morir" means?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.33,1:13:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西班牙语\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's Spanish.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.17,1:13:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思是“我不想死”\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It means "I don't want to die."
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.20,1:13:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认为那些鬼魂跟你说话是想要什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What do you think these ghosts want when they talk to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.94,1:13:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你想一想，科尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I want you to think about it, Cole.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.65,1:13:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你仔细想一想\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I want you to think about it really carefully.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.25,1:13:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认为他们想要什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What do you think they want?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.70,1:13:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要帮助\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Just help.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.90,1:13:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，我也是这么想的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's right. That's what I think too.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.16,1:13:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们只想要帮助，连那些吓人的也是\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They just want help, even the scary ones.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.10,1:13:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我可能知道一个办法，让他们走开\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I think I might know a way to make them go away.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.90,1:13:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.62,1:13:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听他们说\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Listen to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.71,1:13:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万一他们不想要帮忙呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What if they don't want help?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.02,1:14:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万一他们就是生气，就是想伤害别人呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What if they're just angry and they just want to hurt somebody?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.65,1:14:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为事情不会是这样的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't think that's the way it works.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.98,1:14:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么能确定？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How do you know for sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.06,1:14:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不确定\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.35,1:14:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.40,1:15:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走开\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.56,1:15:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这是怎么了？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What's happening to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.42,1:15:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在伤害你？我要揍扁他们\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Is someone hurting you? I'll kick their ass.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.56,1:15:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科尔，要是他们伤害你...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cole, if they're hurting you...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.32,1:15:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 你睡吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mama, you sleep now.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.02,1:17:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在觉得好多了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm feeling much better now.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.34,1:18:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想告诉我什么事吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Do you want to tell me something?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.16,1:18:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她跑了很远的路来找我，对吧？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}She came a long way to visit me, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.46,1:18:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想是的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I guess she did.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.17,1:19:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能拿杯水吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Can you get some water?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.24,1:19:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是她妹妹\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's her sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.00,1:19:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道，我父亲得癌症时我就经历过了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know, when I went through this with my father's cancer...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.23,1:20:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都不能想象一个孩子卧床两年\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I just can't imagine a child being in bed for two years.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.13,1:20:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看过多少医生？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How many... How many doctors?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.33,1:20:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我想有六个了 - 六个不同的医生？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- I think it was six. - Six different doctors?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.34,1:20:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想是的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I think so, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.65,1:20:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我刚听说...小的那个现在也病了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I just heard the, uh, little one is falling ill now.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.21,1:20:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿上帝帮助他们\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}God help them.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.95,1:20:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别回家，好吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't go home, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.71,1:20:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I definitely won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.56,1:22:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mister?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.04,1:22:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了，先生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Excuse me, mister.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.64,1:23:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是琪拉的爸爸吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Are you Kyra's daddy?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.63,1:23:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是给你的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.30,1:23:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她...她想告诉你一件事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Sh-She wanted to tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.23,1:24:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，他来了，他正朝我走过来呢\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, no, here he comes. He's coming my way. Psst!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.60,1:24:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想跳舞吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Would you like to dance?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.41,1:24:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，其实，我只是跟朋友一起来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, actually, I just came with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.51,1:24:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，那么，这样如何？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, well, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.27,1:24:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们先跳一下\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We can dance for a little bit, and
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.01,1:24:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你不喜欢我跳的，你可以踢我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}if you don't like the way I dance, you can kick me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.55,1:24:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃，那好吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, okay then.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.86,1:25:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该吃午餐了，琪拉\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's time for lunch, Kyra.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.34,1:25:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我现在觉得好多了  - 太好了，宝贝\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-I'm feeling much better now. - That's so great, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.42,1:25:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该吃饭了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's time for your food.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.35,1:25:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吃完以后可以出去玩吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Can I go outside if I eat this?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.50,1:25:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道，你知道下午你就病得厉害\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't know. You know how you get sick in the afternoons.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.62,1:25:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再说吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.45,1:26:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说吃起来很奇怪，你知道我不爱听这话\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't say that it tastes funny. You know I don't like to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.13,1:26:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨米的妈妈打过电话\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Tami's mom called.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.65,1:26:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直让她病着\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You were keeping her sick.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.94,1:26:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢它，她说过\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You liked it, she said.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.61,1:26:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她保护着你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}She looked out for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.94,1:26:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琪拉要回来了吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Is Kyra coming back?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.32,1:26:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再也不会了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.83,1:27:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我觉得够了，妆化好了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Ya, I think that's enough. That's enough makeup.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.75,1:27:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.20,1:27:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们在叫马僮了  - 我们得赶快了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- They're calling for the stable boy. - We have to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.43,1:27:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你...你刚刚跟谁说话？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Who, uh... Who were you talking to?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.60,1:27:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是在练习台词\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Just practicing my lines.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.03,1:27:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你给我这个角色，坎宁安先生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thanks for giving me this part, Mr. Cunningham.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.38,1:27:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗，我在这上学时，剧院这里发生过一次大火\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know, when I went to school here, there was a terrible fire in this section of the theater.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.47,1:27:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们重建了整个地方\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They rebuilt the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.66,1:27:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，我知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.78,1:28:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有心灵纯洁的人，才能拔出石中剑\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Only he who is pure of heart can take the sword from the stone.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.71,1:28:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让那孩子试试\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Let the boy try.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.62,1:28:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是个马僮，跟在马后头清扫的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He is a stable boy. He cleans up after the horses.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.53,1:28:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安静，蠢村夫\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Silence, village idiot.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.82,1:28:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让那孩子上前来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Let the boy step forward.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.63,1:28:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万岁，亚瑟王\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hail, King Arthur!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.33,1:29:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你真的演得很棒，科尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I thought you were really great in the play, Cole.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.57,1:29:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 真的？  - 是的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Really? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.10,1:29:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗，还有...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know what else?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.60,1:29:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.75,1:29:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得汤米·汤马西诺烂透了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I thought Tommy Tammisimo sucked big time.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.15,1:29:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有个办法让你跟你妻子说话\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I got an idea how you can talk to your wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.12,1:29:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等她睡着了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Wait till she's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.92,1:29:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她就会听进你的话，不知不觉中\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Then she'll listen to you and she won't even know it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.60,1:30:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再见到你了，是不是？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm not gonna see you anymore, am I?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.00,1:30:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我们要说的都说过了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I think we said everything we needed to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.33,1:30:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许是时候和你更亲近的人说说了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Maybe it's time to say things to someone closer to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.38,1:30:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许我们可以假装明天还要见面\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Maybe we can pretend like we're gonna see each other tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.86,1:30:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是假装\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Just for pretend.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.17,1:30:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.00,1:30:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在要走了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm gonna go now.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.58,1:30:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天见，科尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'll see you tomorrow, Cole.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.34,1:31:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事，警官，我没事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm okay, Officer.I-I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.87,1:31:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道是怎么回事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.43,1:31:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊，希望没有人受伤\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Geez, I hope nobody got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.80,1:31:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很安静\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're very quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.96,1:31:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在气我错过了演出，对吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're mad I missed the play, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.53,1:31:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有两份工作，宝贝\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I have two jobs, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.80,1:31:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道对我们有多重要\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know how important they are for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.84,1:31:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是能去，我愿付出所有\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'd give anything to have been there.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.12,1:32:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在准备好跟你交流了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm ready to communicate with you now.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.76,1:32:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交流？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Communicate?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.40,1:32:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你我的秘密\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Tell you my secrets.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.36,1:32:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.63,1:32:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那边有事故吧？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know the accident up there?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.40,1:32:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.56,1:32:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人受伤了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Someone got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.67,1:32:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They did?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.85,1:32:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一位女士\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A lady.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.45,1:32:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她死了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}She died.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.86,1:32:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊，怎么你能看见她？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, my God. What, you can see her?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.85,1:32:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.48,1:32:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在哪里？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.40,1:32:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就站在我的车窗旁边\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Standing next to my window.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.40,1:33:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科尔，你吓着我了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cole, you're scaring me.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.41,1:33:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时他们也吓着我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They scare me too sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.41,1:33:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.75,1:33:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鬼魂\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.83,1:33:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看得见鬼魂，科尔？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You see ghosts, Cole?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.50,1:33:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们要我替他们做事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They want me to do things for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.05,1:33:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们...他们跟你说话？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They... They talk to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.26,1:33:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们叫你做事情？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They tell you to do things?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.57,1:33:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前就是他们伤害我的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They're the ones that used to hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.00,1:33:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么，妈妈？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What are you thinking, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.50,1:33:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认为我是怪胎？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You think I'm a freak?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.56,1:33:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着我的脸\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Look at my face.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.60,1:33:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不会那么想你，永远不会\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I would never think that about you. Ever.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.00,1:33:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 懂了吗？  - 懂了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Got it? - Got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.55,1:34:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,容我想一想\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Just let me think for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.51,1:34:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外婆跟你问好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Grandma says hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.10,1:34:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说她很抱歉拿走了大黄蜂链坠\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}She says she's sorry for taking the bumblebee pendant.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.45,1:34:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她只是太喜欢它了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}She just likes it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.43,1:34:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.02,1:34:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外婆有时会来看我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Grandma comes to visit me sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.70,1:34:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科尔，这样很不对\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cole, that's very wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.52,1:34:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外婆过世了，这你知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Grandma's gone, you know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.26,1:34:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.68,1:34:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 她要我告诉你...  - 科尔，请别说了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- She wanted me to tell you... - Cole, please stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.41,1:34:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她要我告诉你，她去看你跳舞了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}She wanted me to tell you she saw you dance.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.01,1:34:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说，你小的时候...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}She said when you were little,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.80,1:34:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟她吵过一次架\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}you and her had a fight...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.15,1:34:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在你的独舞表演之前\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}right before your dance recital.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.26,1:34:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为她没来看你跳舞\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You thought she didn't come to see you dance.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.75,1:35:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她看了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}She did.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.11,1:35:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她躲在后面，那样你就看不见她\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}She hid in the back so you wouldn't see.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.21,1:35:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她...她说你就像个天使\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Sh-She said you were like an angel.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.65,1:35:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}She said...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.50,1:35:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你曾来到埋葬她的地方\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}you came to the place where they buried her,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.21,1:35:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问了她一个问题\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}asked her a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.23,1:35:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说，答案是...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}She said the answer is...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.85,1:35:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每一天\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.14,1:35:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你问了她什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What did you ask?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.80,1:35:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Do...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.00,1:35:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有没有令她骄傲？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Do I make her proud?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.96,1:36:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.07,1:36:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}大家好，正如你们多数人都知道的，我...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hi, everybody. As most of you know, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.43,1:36:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我并不习惯讲话\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm not used to doing this,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.33,1:36:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}而且，我答应过安娜不会让她受窘\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and I promised Anna that I'd try not to embarrass her.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.54,1:36:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}这任务就交给她母亲吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'll leave that to her mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.11,1:36:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}不过，我们的确要感谢你们大家到来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But we do want to thank all of you for coming...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.31,1:36:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}并与我们分享这美妙的日子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and for sharing this wonderful day with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.71,1:36:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}对我几乎是苦乐交加，因为我不想把她交出去\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's bittersweet almost, for me, 'cause I hate giving her up.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.63,1:36:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安娜\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Anna?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.83,1:37:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I miss you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.50,1:37:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I miss you too.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.72,1:37:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么，马尔科姆？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Why, Malcolm?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.97,1:37:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.62,1:37:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么事...  - 你为何离开我？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- What is it? - Why did you leave me?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.14,1:37:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有离开你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I didn't leave you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.34,1:37:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看见的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I see people.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.54,1:38:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不知道自己死了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They don't know they're dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.70,1:38:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你多常见到他们？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How often do you see them?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.10,1:38:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时时刻刻\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}All the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.82,1:38:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们无处不在\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They're everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.90,1:38:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们只看得到他们想看的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They only see what they want to see.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.21,1:38:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，麦克\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Okay, Mikey.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.95,1:38:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，给我一分钟\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Come on. Give me a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.92,1:39:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.50,1:39:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不是很痛  - 让我看看\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- It doesn't even hurt. - Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.93,1:39:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看，把手拿开\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Let me see. Put your hand...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.20,1:39:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.14,1:39:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，好了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.50,1:40:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我没事，真的，我觉得只是穿过去了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I think I'm okay. Really, I think it just went...went in and out.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.20,1:40:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在连疼也不疼了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It doesn't even hurt anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.70,1:40:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我现在可以走了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I think I can go now.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.96,1:40:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是需要做几件事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I just needed to do a couple things.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.56,1:40:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要帮助一个人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I needed to help someone.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.70,1:41:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我做到了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I think I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.03,1:41:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还要告诉你一些事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And I needed to tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.57,1:41:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你从来不是第二位的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You were never second.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.96,1:41:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Ever.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.62,1:41:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.85,1:41:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你睡吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You sleep now.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.00,1:41:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了早上一切都会不一样\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Everything will be different in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.93,1:41:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安，马尔科姆\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good night, Malcolm.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.50,1:41:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安，亲爱的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good night, sweetheart.


